data.description: Freshly painted interior in a soft agreeable gray with white baseboards and doors. All appliances have been updated to stainless steel and the home has been cleaned and vacated. Ready for it's new owners is this 3 bed 2 bath home in Berkley Manor, exellent location close to dining,shopping, and all big box stores.Tile floors throughout so no dirty carpet, cathedral ceilings in the living room for that grand entrance when you enter the front door, large primary bedroom with 2 walk in closets, primary bath has a large soaker tub, walk in shower and a double sink vanity. The back of the home has a built in JennAire grilling station so no more grilling in the rain. Indoor laundry room also has plenty of cabinet storage. Both guest bedrooms have large closets . Call today for a showing
